wikipedia.title: Del the Funky Homosapien
wikipedia.extract: Teren Delvon Jones (born August 12, 1972), better known by his stage name Del the Funky Homosapien (sometimes stylised as Del Tha Funkee Homosapien) or Sir DZL, is an American rapper, record producer, songwriter, and singer.

opinions.details: 这个我问了下朋友，这个中文翻译一直有异议，del到底是delvon名字的缩写还是处理的意思？因此有另一个中文名叫：处理放克乐的智者
